  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Game Boy version of the Super Nintendo game with the same name, which in turn is a version of the exclusive japanese game Panel de Pon.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The story mode takes place in the world of Yoshi's Island, where Bowser and his minions have cursed all of Yoshi's friends. Playing as Yoshi, the player must defeat each of his friends in order to remove the curse. Once all friends have been freed, the game proceeds to a series of Bowser's minions, and then to Bowser himself. During these final matches, the player can select Yoshi or any of his friends to play out the stage.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
